-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftvnews.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F2020116W0020&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GO6xA88r%2B4g6PmjrNIuMcHw%3D&h=28c97ebb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ftvnews.com.tw/news/detail/2020116W0020</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:13:04.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"ffcd5d2dcc2bc73e506561ad1690f41fb8099a30","tid":1826275,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:13:36.000Z","msg":"（新方向）如何令垂死的文宣活動起死回生<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1826045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1826045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d8f69e8bdb850d64b4eadc13ce4a078820e5743e","tid":1826275,"uid":81256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:14:54.000Z","msg":"咁佢無講錯，但詭辯<br />\n<br />\n中國5千年都係帝制<br />\n<br />\n你依家支共相對係比較有自由<br />\n但咁講有咩撚意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bba73f685906c92a6b8746676a3d71721bc5aa","tid":1826275,"uid":36157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:26:48.000Z","msg":"支持全球消滅中囯<br />\n殺盡中囯人"},{"pid":"3a4be2b324b3ffa65b399db4ce44d0813e332a71","tid":1826275,"uid":271857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:35:29.000Z","msg":"大陸人權=溫飽權<br />\n即係動物有得食都可以話有人權。"},{"pid":"b2edd6394b6e54f6b27d59c883db9845c7cbba75","tid":1826275,"uid":14103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:42:04.000Z","msg":"都係嘅 人權組織d人入唔到境已經係最好嘅後果<br />\n以前分分鐘屍都冇埋"},{"pid":"b60a30a9c164bafed44e561b1755ae085f4cec99","tid":1826275,"uid":224066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DWbroO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DWbroO.jpg&h=42dc5cba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9f525f870eb0e0b5d1e02b58d976f9136a2fe23","tid":1826275,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25d640d5676e2